{"lemma":"رِكازٌ","slug":"رِكازٌ","root":"ر.ك.ز","root_slug":"ر-ك-ز","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ك-ز","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n16494"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%83%D8%A7%D8%B2%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ore, where a metal sticks"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n16494","headword_ar":"رِكَازٌ","root":"rkz","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Metal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other mineral;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what God has caused to exist"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakazahu","text_ar":"رَكَزَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHodavahu","text_ar":"اَحْدَثَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1146},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the mines;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tibor","text_ar":"تِبْر"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is created in the earth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakiyzapN","text_ar":"رَكِيزَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) the former is pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rikozapN","text_ar":"رِكْزَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or it is pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakiyzapN","text_ar":"رَكِيزَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ahmad Ibn-Khálid, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieces"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of large size, like"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stones such as are called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jalaAmiyd","text_ar":"جَلَامِيد"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of silver"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of gold,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that are extracted from the earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the mine:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) accord. to the people of El- 'Irák,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any metals"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other minerals:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or [so in the A and Mgh, and accord. to the TA, but in the K “ and, ”]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"buried treasure"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Mgh, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the people of the Time of Ignorance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K:) the first of the significations given above is the primary one: and ancient wealth [buried in the earth] is likened to metals or minerals: or, accord. to certain of the people of El- Hijáz, it signifies specially"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"property buried by men before the period of El-Islám;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and not metals or other minerals. (TA.) It is said in a trad., that the fifth part of what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rikaAzN","text_ar":"رِكَازٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is for the government-treasury: (S, * TA:) or, accord. to another relation, of what is termed ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakiyzN","text_ar":"رَكِيزٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": as though it [the latter] were pl. [or rather coll. gen. n.] of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakiyzapN","text_ar":"رَكِيزَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", or [the former] of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rikaAzapN","text_ar":"رِكَازَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","A","Mgh","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%B1%D9%83%D8%A7%D8%B2/","headword_ar":"ركاز","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23291#1533f7","body_html":"<span>الركاز: هو المال المركوز في الأرض، مخلوقًا كان أو موضوعًا.</span>"}]}}